#align category_theory.limits.preserves_colimit_right_op CategoryTheory.Limits.preservesColimitRightOp

/-- If `F : Cᵒᵖ ⥤ Dᵒᵖ` preserves limits of `K.op : Jᵒᵖ ⥤ Cᵒᵖ`, then `F.unop : C ⥤ D` preserves
