#align category_theory.limits.perserves_colimits_op CategoryTheory.Limits.perservesColimitsOp

/-- If `F : C ⥤ Dᵒᵖ` preserves limits, then `F.left_op : Cᵒᵖ ⥤ D` preserves colimits. -/
