#align category_theory.limits.preserves_colimits_left_op CategoryTheory.Limits.preservesColimitsLeftOp

/-- If `F : Cᵒᵖ ⥤ D` preserves limits, then `F.right_op : C ⥤ Dᵒᵖ` preserves colimits. -/
